class=\"ltx_tag ltx_tag_ref\">4.3.3 </span>Impact of layer-dependent progressive parameter.</span></a></li>\n239\t<li class=\"ltx_tocentry ltx_tocentry_subsubsection\"><a href=\"#S4.SS3.SSS4\" title=\"In 4.3 Ablation Studies ‣ 4 Experimental Results ‣ Precise Video-to-Audio Generation with Cross-Modal Alignment in Latent Space\" class=\"ltx_ref\"><span class=\"ltx_text ltx_ref_title\"><span class=\"ltx_tag ltx_tag_ref\">4.3.4 </span>Handling noise in SoundCap.</span></a></li>\n240\t<li class=\"ltx_tocentry ltx_tocentry_subsubsection\"><a href=\"#S4.SS3.SSS5\" title=\"In 4.3 Ablation Studies ‣ 4 Experimental Results ‣ Precise Video-to-Audio Generation with Cross-Modal Alignment in Latent Space\" class=\"ltx_ref\"><span class=\"ltx_text ltx_ref_title\"><span class=\"ltx_tag ltx_tag_ref\">4.3.5 </span>Zero-shot Performance.</span></a></li>\n241\t</ol>\n242\t</li>\n243\t</ol>\n244\t</li>\n245\t<li class=\"ltx_tocentry ltx_tocentry_section\"><a href=\"#S5\" title=\"In Precise Video-to-Audio Generation with Cross-Modal Alignment in Latent Space\" class=\"ltx_ref\"><span class=\"ltx_text ltx_ref_title\"><span class=\"ltx_tag ltx_tag_ref\">5 </span>Conclusion</span></a></li>\n246\t<li class=\"ltx_tocentry ltx_tocentry_bibliography\"><a href=\"#bib\" title=\"In Precise Video-to-Audio Generation with Cross-Modal Alignment in Latent Space\" class=\"ltx_ref\"><span class=\"ltx_text ltx_ref_title\">References</span></a></li>\n247\t</ol></nav>\n248\t</nav>\n249\t<div class=\"ltx_page_main\">\n250\t<div id=\"infobox\" class=\"infobox\">\n251\t  <a id=\"license-tr\" href=\"https://info.arxiv.org/help/license/index.html#licenses-available\">\n252\t    License: CC BY-SA 4.0\n253\t  </a>\n254\t  <div id=\"watermark-tr\">\n255\tarXiv:2607.06405v1 [cs.MM] 07 Jul 2026</div>\n256\t</div><div class=\"ltx_page_content\">\n257\t<article class=\"ltx_document ltx_authors_1line\"><span id=\"id1\" class=\"ltx_note ltx_role_institutetext\"><sup class=\"ltx_note_mark\">1</sup><span class=\"ltx_not