o, Rongjie Huang, Jiawei Huang, Zehan Wang, Fuming You, Ruiqi Li, Zhou Zhao | rank=2 | id=qn2x8a1zXr]\n  3. Frieren: Efficient Video-to-Audio Generation Network with Rectified Flow Matching\n     https://openreview.net/forum?id=prXfM5X2Db\n     [authors=Yongqi Wang, Wenxiang Guo, Rongjie Huang, Jiawei Huang, Zehan Wang, Fuming You, Ruiqi Li, Zhou Zhao | rank=3 | id=prXfM5X2Db]\n\n=== exa (3 results) ===\n  1. Precise Video-to-Audio Generation with Cross-Modal Alignment in ...\n     https://arxiv.org/html/2607.06405v1\n     Frieren employ the same pretrained encoder for video feature extraction that serves as the backbone for the Align Acc metric. This overlap may ...\n  2. Frieren: Efficient Video-to-Audio Generation Network with Rectified ...\n     https://github.com/cyanbx/Frieren-V2A\n     For alignment accuracy, we convert the audio generated by the vocoder into a spectrogram and perform calculations. Refer to alignment classifier in Diff-Foley ...\n  3. [PDF] Precise Video-to-Audio Generation with Cross-Modal Alignment in ...\n     https://sightsound.org/papers/2026/Thanh_Tran_Precise_Video-to-Audio_Generation_with_Cross-Modal_Alignment_in_Latent_Space.pdf\n     Frieren and MDSGen utilize the same pretrained encoder as the evaluation metric itself, which potentially inflates their scores.\n\nTotal: 12 results from 4 sources", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "1718203d-6686-4b65-9f15-1ee9f4f04d8a", "uuid": "acee3175-ee24-49c2-8e51-2cd91bde169e", "timestamp": "2026-07-12T03:52:24.020Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "=== arxiv (3 results) ===\n  1. ImageBind: One Embedding Space To Bind Them All\n     https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.05665\n     [authors=Rohit Girdhar, Alaaeldin El-Nouby, Zhuang Liu, Mannat Singh, Kalyan Vasudev Alwala, Armand Joulin, Ishan Misra | published=2023-05-09 | primary_category=cs.CV | id=2305.05665]\n  2. V2A-Mapper: A Lightweight Solution for Vision-to-Audio Generation by Connecting Foundation Models\n     htt